<!-- OVERVIEW -->

<section class="section">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="section-title">

            <h2>Product Overview</h2>

        </div>

        <p>

            Neodymium-Praseodymium Oxide (NdPr Oxide)
            is one of the most important rare earth
            materials used in the manufacture of
            high-performance permanent magnets.

        </p>

        <p>

            NdPr-based magnets are widely used in
            electric vehicles, wind turbines,
            industrial motors, automation systems,
            robotics and advanced electronic devices.

        </p>

        <p>

            As global demand for electrification and
            renewable energy continues to grow,
            NdPr Oxide remains a strategic raw material
            for modern industrial applications.

        </p>

    </div>

</section>

